# 3_backend_app Cursor Rules

1. Read CURSOR.md in this directory first.
2. API contracts must match API_CONTRACTS.md (frontend expects exact paths and shapes).
3. Use NestJS modules: flight, hotel, booking, user, wallet, promo, chat, health.
4. Path prefix /api for all routes.
5. See REQUIREMENTS_AND_GAP_ANALYSIS.md for phased implementation plan.
